message.body: Got a fitness assessment scheduled for Monday after work.
Just finished my assessment. Do u meet w ########? She is very nice. The assessment takes about an hour. Wear something comfortable ib/c she has u do a few exercises.
Yep, that's the name I got. I am both excited and nervous.

It will be fine. Basically you'll get a starting point, which no one likes, and she'll determine a plan to make positive changes. Once we get our plans maybe we can coordinate some workouts during the week.
That would really be great. I'd love to see you more often anyway and I know I'll stick with this more if I work with someone too :-)
Sounds good to me! I was dreading going there today, mainly b/c my appointment was at 8:30 and I was running late, but it went really well and I'm excited to get started!
I'm glad to hear it went well. Makes me feel a little less weird about it. Just wish my hand didn't hurt so much. PT *sucks*!
